---
pageable: true
---

%header
  %section
    %article
      %h1 hello.
      %p
        I’m Amber Aultman, a product designer in Jacksonville, FL. I work at
        = link_to 'Ignite', 'http://ignitewithus.com'
        where I’m helping to create products that shape the way we work. I take on a bit of freelance work here and there and I’m loving my role as Communications Director for
        = link_to 'AIGA Jacksonville.', 'http://jacksonville.aiga.org'
        You can find me on
        = link_to 'Twitter,', 'https://twitter.com/amberaultman'
        = link_to 'Github,', 'https://github.com/amberaultman'
        = link_to 'Dribbble', 'https://github.com/amberaultman'
        and
        = link_to 'Somewhere', 'https://www.somewhere.com/amberaultman'
        or you can
        = link_to 'drop me a line', 'mailto:amber.aultman@gmail.com'
        to say hello.
- page_articles.each do |article|
  %section
    %article
      %h2
        = link_to article.title, article
        %span= article.date.strftime('%b %e')
      = article.body
- if paginate && num_pages > 1
  %section.page-controls
    %article.center
      - if prev_page
        %button.clean
          %i.fa.fa-long-arrow-left
          = link_to 'Previous', prev_page
      - if next_page
        %button.clean
          = link_to 'Next', next_page
          %i.fa.fa-long-arrow-right
